 "display": {
  "title": {
   "translate": "The Cave Kingdoms"
  },
  "subtitle": {
   "text": "Alex's Caves adds 6 biomes underground. Each one is a different world."
  },
  "description": [
   "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
   "  CH.08 · THE CAVE KINGDOMS",
   "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
   "",
   "▸ Alex's Caves adds 6 unique underground biomes.",
   "  Each one has its own ecosystem,",
   "  its own mobs, its own items,",
   "  and its own way of killing you.",
   "",
   "◈ THE SIX CAVE BIOMES",
   "  └ ✦ Magnetic Caves: magnetite ore, floating stone,",
   "    Magnetite Golem (powerful), Magnote mob",
   "    electromagnetic environment disrupts compasses",
   "  └ ✦ Primordial Caves: ancient, overgrown,",
   "    Trilobite (passive), Prehistoric fish, ancient flora",
   "  └ ✦ Abyssal Chasm: deep and vertical,",
   "    Predator (aggressive), extreme fall risk",
   "  └ ✦ Fossilized Caves: dinosaur fossils, bone blocks,",
   "    Brute (powerful melee mob)",
   "  └ ✦ Toxic Caves: mutagen pools, poisonous atmosphere,",
   "    Contaminated mobs (explode on death)",
   "    → NOTE: confirmed namespace alexscaves:nucleeper",
   "  └ ✦ Infernal Rift: hot, lava adjacent,",
   "    Fire Drake (mini-dragon), volcanic blocks",
   "",
   "◈ LOOT HIGHLIGHTS",
   "  └ Magnetic Caves: Magnetite = strong alternative armor",
   "  └ Primordial Caves: prehistoric drops for unique recipes",
   "  └ Toxic Caves: mutagen items for Ch12 alchemical uses",
   "  └ Infernal Rift: Fire Drake scale = heat armor",
   "",
   "▸ The cave systems go deep.",
   "  Some of them connect to the Sculk.",
   "  None of them are safe.",
   "  All of them are worth it.",
   "",
   "▶ Explore 3 different Alex's Caves biomes [check]",
   "▶ Loot a cave-biome-specific chest [check]",
   "",
   "◇ Alex's Caves mobs do not appear in the item database",
   "  by name — use the namespaces: alexscaves:*",
   "  when searching for drop info."
  ],
